Things to do:
=============

* Add support for parsing query data (GET/POST) and cookies from requests
* Add RequestModule that echos the HTTP request
* Add LogModule for displaying log entries
* Add FileModule for delivering disk files
* Use read-write mutex for HTTPServer modules
* Allow more options for binding servers than just port numbers (IP)
* Add support for SSL/TLS & server certificates
* Add support for built-in authentication (OpenID?)
* Allow HTTP modules to be loaded dynamically from object files
* Build installation packages for OSX, Linux, BSD, Solaris & Windows
* Lots more...
